<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>GOMIN Pooljang</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/css/index.css" />
    <script defer src="/static/index.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="index-container-wrap">
      <div class="index-container">
        <%-include('./include/header') %> <%-include('./include/notification')
        %>
        <div class="letter">
          <div class="announcement">
            <img src="/static/images/pool_anno.png" alt="pool" />
            <span>
              잠깐!! <br />
              보내시기 전 개인 정보가 포함되어 있는 지 확인하셨나요?! <br />
              개인 정보 발설 시 고민풀장에서 일체의
              <b>책임을 지지 않습니다!!</b>
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="modal">
            <div class="modal_body">
              <div><img src="/static/images/pool.gif" /></div>
              <div class="login">
                <h2>WELCOME</h2>
                <label>
                  <span>Email</span>
                  <input type="email" />
                </label>
                <br />
                <label>
                  <span>Password</span>
                  <input type="password" />
                </label>
                <p class="forgot-pass">Forgot password?</p>
                <button type="button" class="submit">Sign In</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <form name="login">
            <div class="form-container">
              <!-- 왼쪽에 person 이미지 -->
              <div class="image-container">
                <img src="/static/images/person.png" alt="person" />
              </div>

              <!-- 오른쪽에 입력 폼 -->
              <div class="form-content">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="title"><span>제목</span></label>
                  <input type="text" id="title" name="title" required />
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="date"><span>일시</span></label>
                  <input type="text" id="date" name="date" required />
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="comment"><span>내용</span></label>
                  <textarea
                    id="comment"
                    name="comment"
                    maxlength="200"
                    required
                  ></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">제출</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
